{"tid":860101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你老母用你5000蚊利是錢比你去學英文，你唔學","createTime":"2018-10-13T05:38:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T06:23:57.000Z","uid":132442,"like":0,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"adf6ef23dac59b7ff544c8554d1f01e16e960ea7","tid":860101,"uid":132442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:38:21.000Z","msg":"你本身有一萬蚊利是錢<br />\n你呀媽安排你去B Council 學英文 ，分十年慢慢學。<br />\n你話一定學唔識，同埋會加學費，起碼要用一萬，即係全部利是錢，唔學了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你問你老母點解一定要去B Council，去其他地方唔得嘅，仲平D抵D。你老母話B Council 近屋企，又好似唔錯咁樣。你話遠D都唔怕，最緊要平，同埋可以同時報幾個其他英文班。你老母話，你就算報人地都未必收你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你問你老母點解一定要學英文，你本身識少少中文，你想繼續進修中文，用其中兩千蚊去補燒完就可以了。剩低落黎1千蚊可以報月經學初級日文，用1千蚊學西班牙文，用1千蚊學泡菜文。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你老母話：「做咩啫你，我又唔係唔比錢你學其他野。」<br />\n你答：「我就係唔信你呀，之前又逼我學鋼琴，最後未學到一pat 屎」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你話你死都唔學英文。你老母忽然慈悲為懷，後悔至極，比你學曬所有你想學嘅野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後，你以為你學到中文，日文，西班牙文，泡菜文，點知周新刀冇張利，你根本學唔曬所用野。你畢業去到新加坡發展，發覺原來英文係咁緊要。你安慰自己，去日本教中文都係一條出路，當初自己窮，冇辦法喇，可能就算學好英文都學唔切喇。自己冇父幹，係咁㗎喇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有人話，係你自己蠢啫，平時又用埋曬D on 9 比喻，連登仔科科DSE 拎5星星，一定學得嚟。咁點解當初唔學英文。<br />\n<br />\nD利是錢係你嘅，你有權決定點洗就點洗。你先至唔會比錢D 學店。但係你呀媽唔會咁諗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b59a0112230e14817bd9609a2eadc714bf6f494","tid":860101,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:42:48.000Z","msg":"你阿媽幫你報完british council過多兩年就入去做高層"},{"pid":"d2d9a5aa38ada833c72c064757c6a287c157a903","tid":860101,"uid":5995,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:54:52.000Z","msg":"唔知樓主up乜鳩"},{"pid":"965ef29fc4b6f5c3f9d0fc9a25c5e09644fac4cf","tid":860101,"uid":132442,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1b59a0112230e14817bd9609a2eadc714bf6f494","tid":860101,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:42:48.000Z","msg":"你阿媽幫你報完british council過多兩年就入去做高層"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:58:40.000Z","msg":"咁樣可唔可以賺多D 利是錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd51afc092c72bbcfc15e3ced5f7435e70729b4a","tid":860101,"uid":34469,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T06:00:09.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 又借啲意支持人工島<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd9fb2cb68e66710e0cf2d40ac2da9507fa897b","tid":860101,"uid":132442,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"fd51afc092c72bbcfc15e3ced5f7435e70729b4a","tid":860101,"uid":34469,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T06:00:09.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 又借啲意支持人工島<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T06:03:10.000Z","msg":"想大家諗清楚點解唔學英文咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07bc140fa34f1e8b163ce00e5234f832725cd9b","tid":860101,"uid":127929,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T06:06:20.000Z","msg":"你老母用你5000蚊利是錢比<span style=\"color: red;\">大陸親戚</span>去學英文，你on99答應左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到時如果大陸親戚學唔識要加錢補課，你冇得say no<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後你啲利是就咁送哂比大陸親戚，<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地過橋抽板，你申請破產</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a63d49dee9c71831b6703d3e17ed2542cef699","tid":860101,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bcd9fb2cb68e66710e0cf2d40ac2da9507fa897b","tid":860101,"uid":132442,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"fd51afc092c72bbcfc15e3ced5f7435e70729b4a","tid":860101,"uid":34469,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T06:00:09.000Z","